sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Seu codigo
    participant IDB as IndexedDB
    participant DB as Banco no Disco

    App->>IDB: indexedDB.open(gerenciador-db, 1)
    IDB->>DB: Verificar versao
    DB-->>IDB: Versao atual: 0 (inexistente)

    IDB->>App: onupgradeneeded
    App->>DB: createObjectStore(tarefas)
    App->>DB: createIndex(status)
    App->>DB: createIndex(dataCriacao)

    DB-->>IDB: Upgrade concluido
    IDB->>App: onsuccess
    App->>App: db pronto para uso
